text: Kandry-Kutuy () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kandrinsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 651 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Tuymazy, 7 km from Kandry. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Kandry-Kutuy
